    Hitachi 15mvx Multisync Monitor

   Amiga A2000 / 68030 / 68882
    1mb chip mem, 6 mb fast mem
    ECS graphics / A2320 Display Enhancer
    Kickstart 3.1, Workbench 3.1
    Quantum SCSI HDs
    Smile 17" Flatscreen Multiscan Monitor
